{"tid":2353187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「史上最醜皇帝像」台灣故宮首度展出 觀眾驚呼「醜爆了」！","createTime":"2021-01-04T13:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T13:52:01.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb0940ebba63a2ad28b5a7c4c7e51b6c24d513e","tid":2353187,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f99b139ad47a45f213e59f736029318dfda92e6","tid":2353187,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"你"},{"pid":"a23910b214a9f8e567332b9f6a7368e54fb5572b","tid":2353187,"uid":13503,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hht0UqO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHht0UqO.jpg&h=34d0ef60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b6fa24f6b2425014f4dc1e15b21f11821385138","tid":2353187,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Ym55xr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Ym55xr.gif&h=ddb17859&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b9ec5e16ca44508425e3358d7a213566931400f","tid":2353187,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b6fa24f6b2425014f4dc1e15b21f11821385138","tid":2353187,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Ym55xr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Ym55xr.gif&h=ddb17859&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:49:42.000Z","msg":"你樓上有圖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794f96f83a9316d956a5aa84f5cde8a27e3011ae","tid":2353187,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"冇龜拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca38687b8e6a0d1d9e88e32b82f9feb6f2576a2","tid":2353187,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"國立故宮博物院珍藏了十幅明太祖朱元璋的「醜像」，畫中的開國皇帝朱元璋不是臉上長滿麻子，便是臉型扭曲、尖嘴如豬、下巴突起。故宮小編曾將這些畫作成「有志(痣)青年」放上網站，大陸電影也曾拿此取笑，網友引為奇談。故宮北院元旦開展的帝后畫像展「權力的形狀」，首次展出此一「史上最醜皇帝畫像」&mdash;明太祖坐像。<br />\n<br />\n「權力的形狀&mdash;南薰殿帝后像」精選清代紫禁城南薰殿收藏的帝后像25張，從夏禹王、唐太宗到宋元明等朝代的皇帝與皇后。開幕第一天便吸引不少觀眾「面聖」，許多人看到明太祖朱元璋長滿麻子的「醜像」，大呼「醜爆了」，但還是看得津津有味。故宮另外收藏兩幅明太祖「正常」的畫像，像中的明太祖儀表堂堂、臉上一顆麻子都沒有。展場特地將俊、醜兩張畫像並列，「醜像」顯然更受觀眾歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n此批奇特的帝王「醜像」引來眾多學者好奇，運送故宮國寶來台的故宮耆老索予明、故宮前書畫處處長王耀庭都曾撰文研究。歷年學者研究總共有三種說法，一是「異相說」&mdash;被畫成豬嘴、麻子臉的朱元璋，在古人眼中其實是「天生異相」、天命所歸，長相奇醜反而是「神化」的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n第二種說法是，明太祖微服出巡時，為了混淆視聽，故意請畫師繪製奇形怪狀的「異相」流傳民間、避免遭暗殺。第三種說法則認為，故宮所藏皆為清宮舊藏，這些明太祖「醜相」是清朝為了醜化前朝皇帝的「再創作」。<br />\n<br />\n「權力的形狀」 中有醜得嚇人的皇帝，也有美得驚人的皇后。如...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNgYF6e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNgYF6e.gif&h=6017563e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12660/5145056\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F12660%2F5145056&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuORQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=d2a16783\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/12660/5145056</a>"},{"pid":"5cfbcc28cc51e80114b2852a153821b332a3e21a","tid":2353187,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YAKZ9ZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYAKZ9ZY.jpg&h=5eebd482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故宮收藏了十幅明太祖朱元璋「醜像」，在元旦剛開幕的大展「權力的形狀」首次展出其中一幅。圖／故宮提供<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCA6P0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCA6P0c.jpg&h=d52aa2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故宮收藏了十幅明太祖朱元璋「醜像」，與兩幅明太祖「正常」的畫像。當兩者一起展出，顯然「醜像」(左)比正常畫像(右一)受歡迎。記者陳宛茜／攝影"},{"pid":"64a32bb85026e24cab449ec8303228d0c322c2f2","tid":2353187,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/maxresdefault_rF5I0_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmaxresdefault_rF5I0_1200x0.png&h=a2b8908f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}